<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Mature <i>Chamaecyparis lawsoniana </i>individuals have thick, fire-resistant bark that allows trees to persist through repeated fires (Uchytil 1990d). Stands appear to withstand low- to high-intensity fires, which mainly depend on the understory components and adjacent stand components, at a moderate fire return interval (Skinner et al. 2006).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
